track.name: let me know (I wonder why freestyle)

album.title: Let Me Know (I Wonder Why Freestyle) [Explicit]

wiki.summary: “Let Me Know (I Wonder Why Freestyle)” is a freestyle track featuring Juice singing about a girl that left him, while also pleasing to her to let him know what he can do for her to stay with him. On December 7th, 2019, over two years after its debut on SoundCloud, the song received an official release on streaming platforms, coinciding with the track’s rising popularity on the social media app TikTok. The new version included a cleaner and polished mix than its original version. Read more on Last.fm.
